Yes, ive had that problem before, if you have a bunch of people at a really high level, and they start pking, or they mass, It Resets them, ive been reset on jordiescape too, that was my source, but i would tell them not to max out, a few of my friends told me it overloads, everything and logs them out, and when they try to log in again it just resets them, because they are still logged in, but make sure they dont mass or anything, when i used jordiescape as my source, i was messing around with friends, and they massed, and we had a massing fight, and we all got reset, so i know how it feels, I would add an anti mass feature, but other than that, i really have no idea, i hope i helped you in someway my friend
